<item chapterid="594219" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1928" articlename="冰山女神爱上我" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521472851" lastupdate="1521472851" chaptername="第83章沉重一击" chapterorder="83" size="6394" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    海峰神色冷峻，缓缓道：“你走后冬儿就跟了他，这个人就是――段――祥――龙！”

    我大吃一惊，抬头看着海峰，目瞪口呆：“你――你说什么？”

