<item chapterid="595131" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1928" articlename="冰山女神爱上我" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521472851" lastupdate="1521472851" chaptername="第995章皇者的消息" chapterorder="995" size="6901" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    海珠接着看着我手里的螃蟹：“哎，这么多，你买的？”

