<item chapterid="595234" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1928" articlename="冰山女神爱上我" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521472851" lastupdate="1521472851" chaptername="第1098章养虎为患" chapterorder="1098" size="6608" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    孙东凯继续仰脸看着天花板，眉头不由紧皱起来，自言自语又说了一句：“既然没戏。那会养虎为患的。”

